        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="indent(8)">10</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <placeName>P</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">L.A.</p>
            <pb n="2R"/>
            <p rend="indent(8)">
                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>
                <date>18<hi rend="sup">th</hi> May 1847</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I have been prevented addressing you<lb/> of late by a pressure of
                business however in the interim<lb/> I have learned nothing that would be of
                interest to you<lb/> I was handed the enclosed advertisement for insertion 3<lb/>
                times in the Occident please attend to it if not too late.<lb/> I have yet on hand a
                small amt collected of subscribers<lb/> which I will forward to you by opportunity—I
                am<lb/> instructed by <persName>Mr I Goldberg </persName>and also by <persName>Mr
                    Aub</persName><lb/> to discontinue their Occident, <persName>Mr G</persName>
                does not now live<lb/> in <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> and I saw him but few
                weeks back<lb/>
                <persName>Mr A.</persName> was absent <placeName>East</placeName> when I collected
                his subscription<lb/> or he says he would have told me before—you will please<lb/>
                in future address my brothers numbers to <placeName>Louisville<lb/> Ky</placeName>
                his present residence. You will please put the<lb/> following names on the
                subscription list of the Jewish<lb/> Publication Society—<persName>Alexander
                    Mayer</persName> (care <persName>Harris &amp;<lb/> Abraham</persName>)
                    <persName>Lawrence Bruel</persName> (care <persName>Harris &amp;
                    Abraham</persName>)<lb/>
                <persName>Samuel Mayer</persName> (care <persName>Arnold Springer &amp;
                    Co</persName>) <persName>Joseph Jonas</persName>,<lb/>
                <persName>Daniel Wolf</persName>, and <persName role="author">Lewis
                    Abraham</persName> they are such<lb/> subscribers for the current year from its
                commencement<lb/> and wish all the numbers of this year, I will send<lb/> on their
                subscriptions to you With best wishes I<lb/> am Your friend</p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Lewis Abraham</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
